title: Justin Trudeau elected Canada's prime minister; young liberal star compared to Obama
text: TORONTO (AP) -- Canadian voters reclaimed their country's liberal identity, sending Justin Trudeau -- the son of one of the country's most dynamic politicians -- to the prime minister's office and ending nearly a decade of conservative leadership under Stephen Harper. ...
